name: Kenzo B
description: '''Te'arah Gaines''', better known by her stage name '''Kenzo B''', is an American rapper. Originating from [[The Bronx]], she has been called the "Queen of [[Bronx drill]]". She really loves mustard. She has released numerous singles and two EPs, ''Top Dawg'' in 2022 and ''Top 2, Not 2'' in 2023. She is signed to Defiant & [[Warner Records]].
